  "Frequently Asked Questions",
  "AICTE Internship Portal",
  "1. What is the AICTE Internship Portal?",
  "The AICTE Internship Portal is a National Internship Platform to connect students with verified companies, startups, MSMEs, and organizations offering internships, apprenticeships, PPOs, and skill-based opportunities across India.",
  "2. Is the AICTE Internship Portal free for students?",
  "Yes, the AICTE Internship Portal is free of cost for students to register, create profiles, and apply for internships.",
  "3. What types of internships are available on the AICTE Internship Portal?",
  "The portal offers internships in 200+ domains, including engineering, management, IT, marketing, finance, healthcare, research, artificial intelligence, data science, government projects, and many others.",
  "4. Are internships on the portal verified?",
  "Yes, the portal connects students with verified companies, startups, MSMEs, and organizations to ensure transparency and trusted opportunities.",
  "5. Does the portal provide paid internships?",
  "Yes, both paid and unpaid internships are available on the AICTE Internship Portal, depending on the company and role.",
  "6. How does the AICTE Internship Portal help colleges?",
  "The portal helps colleges track student internships, strengthen industry-academia collaboration, and support practical learning and skill development.",
  "7. Are remote internships available on the portal?",
  "Yes, many organizations offer remote, hybrid, and work-from-home internships through the AICTE Internship Portal.",
  "8. How does the AICTE Internship Portal support skill development?",
  "The portal promotes “Learning by Doing” by helping students gain practical industry experience, improve technical skills, and build career-ready expertise through real-world projects and internships.",
  "The AICTE Internship Portal is transforming the way students connect with industry by creating a powerful bridge between academic education and real-world professional experience. The platform connects students with verified companies, startups, MSMEs, and organizations across India, enabling them to gain industry exposure, develop practical skills, and prepare for future careers through internships, apprenticeships, and PPOs (Pre-Placement Offers).",
  "It helps students understand how industries, organizations, and professional work environments operate before entering the workforce. By offering hands-on experience, real-time projects, and industry interaction, the platform empowers students to build technical expertise, communication abilities, problem-solving skills, and workplace confidence. With verified company onboarding, candidate matching, authenticated student profiles, and seamless collaboration between students, colleges, and recruiters, the AICTE Internship Portal creates a trusted, transparent, and future-ready internship ecosystem across India.",
